node.title: Recap Super Rugby: Crusaders v Highlanders
node.description: The Crusaders have beaten the Highlanders 17-14 in the 2022 Super Rugby Pacific competition at OrangeTheory Stadium in Christchurch. See how the action unfolded with Jamie Wall.
